Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配備著以電腦為導航系統的賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「CYBER F0RMULA」正式登場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.39,0:00:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替「F-l」的2l世紀賽車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.17,0:00:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令全世界人都狂熱起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,新世紀GPX 「CYBER F0RMULA」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.08,0:00:33.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:40.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:43.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的悸動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:47.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自你求助的訊號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:53.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨夜開始一直感覺得到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:01:00.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突如其來的風暴阻擋了前進的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:04.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望便浮現在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:08.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜歡 是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.51,0:01:15.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會放在心上 不論什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:20.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的波浪會緊隨而來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:27.79,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在馬上出發 決不動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:33.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了實現夢想 永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.58,0:01:36.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:43.74,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快快出發 不用有任何擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:50.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫助你 因為喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.68,0:01:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人所屬的管生阿斯拉達隊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正朝向巴西的新裏約
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.68,0:02:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備參加世界賽的第三戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個場地直線很多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.82,0:02:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何在這個彎道超車\N是比賽的重點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了\N關鍵就在於如何運用煞車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼?伸介
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大樓風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.67,0:02:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風勢相當的強勁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下子我看是有點棘手了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是風大了點嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且阿斯拉達的尾翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是剛好可以藉著風的阻力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加它的貼地性嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 在接近極速的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制阻力太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕速度會沒有辦法加快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.69,0:02:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果改變尾翼的角度的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而可能會被風吹翻的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔他說這次比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把車子改成高速用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.23,0:02:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介 你認為\N車田叔這個提議可行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是典型的高速場地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然這麼做很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一定有很好的效果的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十七話  友情演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 你看起來蠻高興的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.46,0:03:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是等一下有約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 怎麼會有人跟我約會嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.23,0:03:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算有的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可比約會還重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.81,0:03:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 風怎麼這麼強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.98,0:03:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把路面檢查過後馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.69,0:03:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.52,0:03:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把阿斯拉達改裝成高速用車
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.23,0:03:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風阻零件還有高速的引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概中午左右就會到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:03:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要準備一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說上午就要開始工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離預賽只剩下三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要在預賽之前完工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次無論如何一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓隼人上頒獎台去領獎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再開始可不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.05,0:04:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦 你是不是有事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零件到了以後就開始好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良平 你也是一樣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:30.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次就看我們的好了 對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看 還是跟車田叔說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾翼沒有調整
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三戰的場地尾翼的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是影響勝敗的關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身為職業的維修員\N應該知道這點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:04:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新條先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的失誤就是我的過失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是希望你們來道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是希望你們做事情\N要像一個職業維修員而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家回去工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要上了一次頒獎台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後就不想下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的賽車手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.19,0:05:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是希望如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了達到這個目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們不需要工作能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達不到要求的工作人員
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.93,0:05:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的事情就交給我來辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 如果沒有我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會得到第三名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.81,0:05:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好神氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.89,0:06:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我沒有認錯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不就是\N阿斯拉達隊的維修隊長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想請問你想不想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我這裏工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像阿斯拉達這種弱的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能夠拿到第五名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可見你的技術是相當的不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且像那種犯錯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.15,0:06:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒挺不客氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了 我這樣做不對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維修員雖然有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我對你的評價特別的高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你肯的話\N隨時都歡迎你過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 零件都到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢說我們是弱隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什麼人都會有自尊心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 開始工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 其他的工作就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介把場地資料輸進電腦裏面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔 有點事想跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日期就是今天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格利合唱團
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美樹是他們的忠實歌迷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介 你對搖滾樂很熟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不熟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種熱鬧的音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的沒有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這個合唱團的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.46,0:08:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新裏歐足球場今晚七點鐘開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪美樹一副心不在焉的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美樹這個丫頭這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛不告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美樹的責任感非常強
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過聽個演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也花不了多少時間嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是肯讓她\N去聽演唱會了是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:51.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從出發以後都太緊張了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是美樹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有必要輕鬆一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到車田叔還有輕鬆的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫沒想到 真是太過份了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我 光是懂得電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他都一竅不通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是車田叔的話\N我根本就不可能在這
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美樹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.22,0:09:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要去聽演唱會你就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說的都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才買到的票
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要浪費了 聽到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是良平這小子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說我是很想去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了?可是票都已經買好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔肯讓我去我心領了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定我不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美樹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是人沒有不犯錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:10:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是把人當做機器一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就太過份了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.59,0:10:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人到底是誰呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意演唱會的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到鼓舞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呀 一年前管生阿斯拉達隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,招募新人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是我跟美樹剛進來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是一個無名小卒的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以根本就沒有人來應徵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候美樹她跟我說過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒有人來應微
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個隊伍不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介 怎麼辦 你想留下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.11,0:10:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非老闆說他要解敵這個隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則的話我是不會走的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:11:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目標是要做一個\N世界級的維修員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要有隊伍招人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就去應微
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.99,0:11:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不管到那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說太年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說女孩子不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時非常的沮喪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個全部由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子組成的\N搖滾合唱團格利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:23.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候我聽了她們的歌之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我受到很大的鼓勵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個歌詞我到現在都還沒忘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌詞是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得自己信心十足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要再試一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個合唱團就在這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呀 當時車田叔跟經理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只問我想不想做維修員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的一律沒有提
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就決定要留下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到解敵為止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣所以才那麼想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就更該去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 現在去還來得及嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽好 良平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是維修員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是做好車子的維修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去聽啊 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就交給我來做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一邊工作一邊在想這個事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:13:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是在葵車隊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就被開除了你知不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.41,0:13:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵車隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算賽車的成績再不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.44,0:13:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可以把責任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸罪於維修員的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想美樹她一定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想去聽演唱會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.92,0:13:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她又不去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又有什麼辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 還有明白香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個幫我個忙好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介 我們的運氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的還蠻不錯的\N居然買到票了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用電腦預約的剛好有五張退票
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運氣不錯可以完成美樹心願了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真怕被美樹知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們偷偷跑去幫她買票的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩個人一做起事情來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對週遭的事情完全都不顧的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介 開快點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介 快點準備錄音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 把這個戴上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.41,0:15:26.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:27.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視台的臂章啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱會是不准錄音的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就假裝要採訪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經跟主辦單位聯絡過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是向電視台的人借的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是伸介
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼人 你負責右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左側呢由明日香來負責
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.50,0:15:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算把引擎給弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個維修員他真的被解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解雇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是葵隊的維修員
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 大家好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一首曲子是埋所當然的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 大家都跑到那裏去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:16:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是道地的巴西咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事讓我來做就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們裝引擎也夠累的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子情況現在怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的明天一天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以全部做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天我也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們去那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒去那
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 菜愈燒愈好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的薯泥很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.11,0:17:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實那是隼人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.08,0:17:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介在叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有很重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟他說我吃完飯\N馬上就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看啊還是拿到裏面吃好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什麼鬼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.71,0:18:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管了 快點來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙控器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 請你慢慢的欣賞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.65,0:18:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你們就到了演唱會現場
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車田叔 你說他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去買東西的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過是在\N遵照大家的指示行事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望她會喜歡那個禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她絕對不會失望的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸介這小子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到他還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.53,0:21:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美樹跟伸介剛剛來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我跟我老闆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要再度跟我們理想挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然大家都想要試試看\N那我們就試試啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當時也是為了美樹的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要留下那句話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才留在這裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都有他的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會有現在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.61,0:21:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是為了將來能夠\N跟大家一起創造美好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良平 吃完飯開始工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.46,0:21:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美樹 你慢慢欣賞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然現在有錄影帶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都可以看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.79,0:22:16.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他人目光沒有在背後注視著我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.45,0:22:23.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面向前方 生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:27.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為肩負著使命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:37.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放下雙手 仰望天空時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:40.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互信任
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:48.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑容是我心中的支柱
